originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.p_name AS part_name, 
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS order_count, 
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue, 
    r.r_name AS region_name, 
    n.n_name AS nation_name
FROM 
    part p
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    p.p_type LIKE '%BRASS%'
    AND o.o_orderdate BETWEEN '1994-01-01' AND '1994-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    p.p_name, r.r_name, n.n_name
HAVING 
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) > 10000
ORDER BY 
    total_revenue DESC, part_name ASC

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."PART_NAME", "t5"."PART_NAME") AS "PART_NAME", "t5"."ORDER_COUNT", "t5"."TOTAL_REVENUE", "t5"."REGION_NAME", "t5"."NATION_NAME"
FROM (SELECT MIN("part"."p_name") AS "PART_NAME", COUNT(DISTINCT "orders"."o_orderkey") AS "ORDER_COUNT", SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE", MIN("region"."r_name") AS "REGION_NAME", MIN("s1"."n_name") AS "NATION_NAME"
FROM "part"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineitem"."l_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "s1"."n_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "region" ON "s1"."n_regionkey" = "region"."r_regionkey"
WHERE "part"."p_type" LIKE '%BRASS%' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" >= '1994-01-01' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" <= '1994-12-31'
GROUP BY "part"."p_name", "region"."r_name", "s1"."n_name"
HAVING SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) > 10000.0000
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST, 1) AS "t5"

SELECT COALESCE("r_regionkey", "r_regionkey") AS "r_regionkey", "r_name", "r_comment"
FROM "region"

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."PART_NAME", "t5"."PART_NAME") AS "PART_NAME", "t5"."ORDER_COUNT", "t5"."TOTAL_REVENUE", "t5"."REGION_NAME", "t5"."NATION_NAME"
FROM (SELECT MIN("part"."p_name") AS "PART_NAME", COUNT(DISTINCT "orders"."o_orderkey") AS "ORDER_COUNT", SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE", MIN("s1"."r_name") AS "REGION_NAME", MIN("nation"."n_name") AS "NATION_NAME"
FROM "part"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineitem"."l_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "nation"."n_regionkey" = "s1"."r_regionkey"
WHERE "part"."p_type" LIKE '%BRASS%' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" >= '1994-01-01' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" <= '1994-12-31'
GROUP BY "part"."p_name", "s1"."r_name", "nation"."n_name"
HAVING SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) > 10000.0000
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST, 1) AS "t5"
